To interact with decentralized applications you must have a tron wallet that support TronWeb / dapps.

Example: TronWallet.me is a bridge for allowing TRON DApps to run in the browser without having to deploy a TRON Full Node. This allows for the web DApp to interact with the TRON network.

Perodium supported wallets: https://perodium.com/wallets

TronNetwork wallets list: https://tron.network/wallet
